### Sales Cycle Evaluation

**Must evaluate alongside:**
- Average deal size (longer cycles acceptable for larger deals)
- Win rate (faster isn't better if conversion suffers)
- Customer quality (strategic clients worth longer cycles)

**Red flags:**
- Cycle lengthening without deal size increase
- High variance (unpredictable timing)
- Consistent delays at same stage

