### Funnel Health Indicators

**Healthy funnel:**
- Consistent conversion at each stage
- Predictable progression timing
- High SQL quality (low proposal waste)

**Unhealthy funnel:**
- Wide variance stage-to-stage
- Long stall periods between stages
- High early-stage volume, low late-stage conversion

